snippet.title: Amiga Longplay Lotus III: The Ultimate Challenge
snippet.description:
http://www.recordedamigagames.org

Played By: RickyC

I liked the first two games more than this. Something about this game that just wasnt as great :O 

I played the first 6 races with the music tracks on but then just left them off for the sound effects to be on. The music i love and i wish you could of had both playing at the same time D: Dont like how impossible the windy level was! -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
